<ul>
<li>Minimum boning, only to make a shell of the garment.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Skills you gain:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Basic skills of sewing on the boning;</li>
<li>How to make curvy forms of the corset and the cups;</li>
<li>How to adjust the pattern to different sizes and body types.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Where to use:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Perfect for young fashion;</li>
<li>Corsets for a light waist reduction;</li>
<li>Great as a base for drapery for corsets and dresses.</li>
</ul>
